title: Apocalyptic Forecast
description: Life never seems to go Huai Shi's way. No friends, no family, no money... And when he tries to get a job with his cello at a club, he almost becomes a gigolo! This is no way for a main character with a cheat code to live... But when the supernatural finally starts catching up with him, he begins to wish it never did.
author: Moonlight Breeze
